OL,3,CMan sentenced to life after murdering
OL,4,Cgirlfriend's brother at birthday party
OL,6,FA man has been sentenced for the
OL,7,Fmurder of his girlfriend's brother at
OL,8,Fa 70th birthday party
OL,10,F42-year-old Stephen Bates was found
OL,11,Fguilty of murder at Liverpool Crown
OL,12,FCourt and has been sentenced to life
OL,13,Fimprisonment with a minimum term of 18
OL,14,Fyears.
OL,16,FMartin O'Donovan died in hospital
OL,17,Fafter being hit by a car on Friday 18
OL,18,FApril in Merseyside, following his
OL,19,Fmother's 70th birthday party.
