OL,3,CMan sentenced to life after murdering
OL,4,Cgirlfriend's brother at birthday party
OL,6,FO'Donovan, 47, was attending the party
OL,7,Falongside Bates when the pair became
OL,8,Finvolved in a drunken argument.
OL,10,FMartin, 47, was attending his mum's
OL,11,F70th birthday party alongside Bates
OL,12,Fwhen the pair became involved in a
OL,13,Fdrunken argument.
OL,15,FBates and Martin O'Donovan were
OL,16,Finitially said to have "hit it off
OL,17,Fstraight away" but later into the
OL,18,Fnight they became embroiled in a
OL,19,Fdrunken fight.
