OL,3,CMan sentenced to life after murdering
OL,4,Cgirlfriend's brother at birthday party
OL,6,FThe defendant had insisted on driving
OL,7,Fhome despite being drunk, but was
OL,8,Ftaken home by a different family
OL,9,Fmember.
OL,11,FHowever, Bates decided to return to
OL,12,Fthe scene and drive his Ford Fiesta
OL,13,Finto O'Donovan before returning to the
OL,14,Fscene and driving his Ford Fiesta into
OL,15,Fthe victim.
OL,17,FMartin was left trapped beneath the
OL,18,Fchassis as a result, with his uncles
OL,19,Fand cousins having to work together in
OL,20,Forder to lift the vehicle up and free
OL,21,Fhim.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
