OL,3,CMan sentenced to life after murdering
OL,4,Cgirlfriend's brother at birthday party
OL,6,FHowever, he subsequently died in
OL,7,Fhospital after suffering serious head
OL,8,Finjuries during the incident.
OL,10,FBates, of Herondale Road in Mossley
OL,11,FHill, meanwhile went on to tell the
OL,12,Fofficers who arrested him: "I know
OL,13,Fwhat I've done, I've f***ed up".
OL,15,FBates was arrested at the scene and
OL,16,Fsubsequently charged with murder, for
OL,17,Fwhich a jury found film guilty.
OL,19,FHe stood with his head bowed and
OL,20,Fshowed no reaction as he was handed
OL,21,Fhis sentence.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
