OL,3,CMan sentenced to life after murdering
OL,4,Cgirlfriend's brother at birthday party
OL,6,FSpeaking after the sentencing,
OL,7,FDetective Chief Inspector Alyson
OL,8,FKeenan said: "What should have been a
OL,9,Fjoyous occasion instead brought
OL,10,Fviolence and then devastation at the
OL,11,Fhands of Stephen Bates.
OL,13,F"Bates was heavily intoxicated and
OL,14,Fothers intervened to prevent him
OL,15,Fdriving, taking him away from the
OL,16,Fgathering. Despite this, Bates
OL,17,Freturned in his car, using it as a
OL,18,Fweapon to fatally injure Martin
OL,19,FO'Donovan, who was sitting outside the
OL,20,Fhouse.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
