OL,3,CMan sentenced to life after murdering
OL,4,Cgirlfriend's brother at birthday party
OL,6,F"Bates showed no remorse throughout
OL,7,Fthe trial, not towards Martin
OL,8,FO'Donovan or anyone else so terribly
OL,9,Faffected by his actions."
OL,11,FPaying tribute to the 47-year-old,
OL,12,FMartin's family said: "Martin was a
OL,13,Fkind, intelligent, generous and deeply
OL,14,Floved man. A brother, son, uncle and
OL,15,Ffriend whose warmth, humour and
OL,16,Fintegrity touched everyone around him.
OL,18,F"His absence has left a hole in our
OL,19,Flives that will never be filled.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
