OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F392A1764347329
OL,3,CMan sentenced to life after murdering
OL,4,Cgirlfriend's brother at birthday party
OL,6,F"The actions that took Martin from us
OL,7,Fwere deliberate, senseless and cruel.
OL,8,FThroughout this process, we have seen
OL,9,Fno sign of remorse from the defendant.
OL,10,FNo acknowledgment of the suffering
OL,11,Fcaused or the life taken, and lives
OL,12,Fdestroyed. That absence of humanity
OL,13,Fhas compounded our grief and made this
OL,14,Fordeal even harder to bear.
OL,16,FThey added: "While today's outcome
OL,17,Fbrings a measure of accountability, it
OL,18,Fcannot bring justice in any true sense.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
