OL,3,CMan sentenced to life after murdering
OL,4,Cgirlfriend's brother at birthday party
OL,6,F"There is no sentence long enough, no
OL,7,Fwords strong enough, to balance the
OL,8,Floss of Martin. We will carry his
OL,9,Fmemory with us always, and our focus
OL,10,Fnow is on honouring the life he lived
OL,11,Frather than the manner in which it was
OL,12,Ftaken."
